{
  "texts": [
    "This data reflects the industrial predictive maintenance scenario with correlated features including several physical quantities.",
    "We use several types of generative methods for time-series as baselines.",
    "At first, we consider autoregressive generative methods: T-Forcing (teacher forcing) [40], [41] and P-Forcing (professor forcing) [42].",
    "Next, we use GAN-based methods: TimeGAN [6], RCGAN [29], C-RNN-GAN [30], COT-GAN [31], GT-GAN [7].",
    "We also test VAE-based methods into our baselines: TimeVAE [5]."
  ]
}